2031}, {\"ngram\": \"thebook\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"McLaughlin-Levrone\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"her past experiences\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2126}, {\"ngram\": \"perfection\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"the ways\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a Christian, I now existed to glorify God (1 Corinthians 6:19-20; Matthew 5:16).\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2227, \"end\": 2236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.999997356208353, \"rank\": 2.6437981992088266e-06, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"(1 Corinthians\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the beginning of 2021, I was learning all the way my life wasn't about me.\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"all the way\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was about showing the world God's power, wisdom, kindness, love, and forgiveness,\\\" she wrote.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2414}, {\"ngram\": \"God's power\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"wisdom\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"kindness\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2444}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2450}, {\"ngram\": \"forgiveness\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were a bunch of different ways to do that.\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bunch\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"different ways\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Off the track, I could do that by serving others, putting their needs before mine, and being excited when God did a remarkable work in their lives (Philippians 2:3-4).\\\"\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2679, \"end\": 2692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippians_2\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippians 2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippians_2\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippians_2\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"their needs\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"mine\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2640}, {\"ngram\": \"a remarkable work\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McLaughlin-Levrone shared how she glorifies God on the track by \\\"running with all my mind and body,\\\" because running \\\"was the gift God gave me to use, and by using it to the best of my ability and humbly redirecting the attention to him, he would be glorified.\\\"\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McLaughlin-Levrone\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2761}, {\"ngram\": \"all my mind\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2790}, {\"ngram\": \"body\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"the gift\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"my ability\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"the attention\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Citing the movieChariots of Fire, which tells the story of Christian sprinter Eric Liddell, McLaughlin-Levrone also acknowledged how \\\"[God] takes pleasure in us doing what we were made for.\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 3153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3023, \"end\": 3032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.999997356208353, \"rank\": 2.6437981992088266e-06, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 3042, \"end\": 3054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.04132827423892e-45, \"text\": \"Eric Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the movieChariots\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2988}, {\"ngram\": \"Fire\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 2996}, {\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"McLaughlin-Levrone\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3074}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"pleasure\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3118}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And win, lose, or draw, to run the race well is to glorify him.\\\"\", \"from\": 3154, \"to\": 3218, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For many Olympians, even those who stand on the gold-medal podium, competing and winning, however satisfying, has proven to be less important than their relationship with God.\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3395, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many Olympians\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"even those\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3250}, {\"ngram\": \"